name: Alex Johnson
summary: Alex Johnson is a 34-year-old non-binary software engineer from Albuquerque, New Mexico who now lives in Los Angeles, California. They are highly educated, having graduated from Stanford University and are fluent in English, Spanish, and German. Alex values honesty, respect, and integrity and enjoys hiking, cooking, and artificial intelligence. Holding liberal political views and identifying as agnostic, they are interested in long term, monogamous relationships. Alex belongs to the Hispanic/Latino ethnicity and uses they/them/their pronouns. They have a dog and a fish, and although they currently don't have children, they desire to have some in the future. Alex prefers a partner who is aged between 28 and 40, and appreciates an active lifestyle similar to theirs. They avoid smoking and drug use and occasionally enjoy a drink. With their Aquarius zodiac sign and their ENTJ personality type, Alex brings a unique perspective to relationships.
